{{Infobox wrestling PPV series |name = Histeria Boricua |image = File:IWA Histeria Boricua logo.jpg |image_size = 250px |caption = IWA Histeria Boricua logo |promotions = IWA |othernames = |nicknames = "La noche donde se sintio la verdadera Euforia" (2008)<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20080208134948if_/http://www.iwapr.tv:80/noticias/474.php]</ref> |firstevent = Histeria Boricua 2000 |lastevent = |gimmick = Season opener }}
'''IWA Histeria Boricua''' is an annual event produced by [[International Wrestling Association (Puerto Rico)|International Wrestling Association]] (IWA) as a season opening event. It has been historically held during the first weeks of January, regularly coinciding with the celebration of [[Epiphany (holiday)|Epiphany]].
==Histeria Boricua 2000== {{Infobox Wrestling event |name=Histeria Boricua |image= |promotion=[[International Wrestling Association (Puerto Rico)|International Wrestling Association]] |date=January 6, 2000 |venue=[[Rubén Rodríguez Coliseum]] |city=[[Bayamón, Puerto Rico]] |attendance= |buyrate= |lastevent= |nextevent= }}The 2000 event was held on January 6, 2000 in [[Bayamón, Puerto Rico]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cagematch.net/?id=1&nr=123424|title=IWA Puerto Rico Histeria Boricua 2000 « Events Database « CAGEMATCH - The Internet Wrestling Database|last=Kreikenbohm|first=Philip|website=www.cagematch.net|access-date=2016-06-11}}</ref>{{Pro Wrestling results table|results=|match1=[[Luna Vachon]] defeated [[Sumie Sakai]]|stip1=[[Singles match]]|match2=[[Kai En Tai]] ([[Taka Michinoku]] and [[Masakatsu Funaki|Funaki]]) defeated Pepe Prado and Andy Anderson|stip2=[[Professional wrestling tag team match types|Tag Team Match]]|match3=[[D-Generation X]] ([[X-Pac]] and [[Billy Gunn]]) defeated [[D'Lo Brown]]|stip3=Handicap Match|match4=[[Val Venis]] and [[Ricky Santana]] defeated [[The Headbangers]] ([[Charles Warrington|Mosh]] & [[Glenn Ruth|Thrasher]]) and [[Savio Vega]] and [[Huracan Castillo]]|stip4=Three Way Tag Team Match for the inaugural [[IWA World Tag Team Championship]]}}{{Clear}}
