e Threat Hardcore Match |- |6 |Victor The Bodyguard defeated Rey Fenix (with Savio Vega & Avbriela) |Singles Match |- |7 |Shane the Glamour Boy (c) defeated [[Jeff Jarrett]] |Singles Match for the [[IWA Intercontinental Heavyweight Championship|IWA Intercontinental Championship]] |- |8 |Ricky Banderas defeated Apolo (c) |Singles Match for the [[IWA Undisputed World Heavyweight Championship|IWA World Heavyweight Championship]] |}
