{{Unreferenced|date=March 2007}}
The '''MYX Music Awards''' is an accolade presented by the cable channel [[Myx]] to honor the biggest hitmakers in the [[Philippines]]. The awards ceremony is held annually and occurs most commonly in the month of March, and broadcast delayed on Myx. MYX viewers from all over the Philippines decide the winners in 17 major categories via [[Short Message Service|SMS]] [[text messaging]] by 2010 it is 60% fan votes through internet and 40% artists votes.
[[Sarah Geronimo]] has the most wins in the history of the awards ceremony.
==Award categories==
===Competitive Awards=== *Myx Music Award for Favorite Music Video {{small|(since 2006)}} *[[Myx Music Award for Favorite Song]] {{small|(since 2006)}} *Myx Music Award for Favorite Artist {{small|(since 2006)}} *Myx Music Award for Favorite New Artist {{small|(since 2006)}} *Myx Music Award for Favorite Rock Video {{small|(since 2006)}} *Myx Music Award for Favorite Urban Video {{small|(since 2006)}} *Myx Music Award for Favorite Mellow Video {{small|(since 2006)}} *Myx Music Award for Favorite Remake {{small|(since 2006)}} *Myx Music Award for Favorite Male Artist {{small|(since 2006)}} *Myx Music Award for Favorite Female Artist {{small|(since 2006)}} *Myx Music Award for Favorite Group {{small|(since 2006)}} *Myx Music Award for Favorite Media Soundtrack {{small|(since 2006)}} *Myx Music Award for Favorite Collaboration {{small|(since 2006)}} *Myx Music Award for Favorite Guest Appearance in a Music Video {{small|(since 2006)}} *[[Myx Music Award for Favorite International Video]] {{small|(since 2006)}} *Myx Music Award for Favorite MYX Celebrity VJ {{small|(since 2007)}} *Myx Music Award for Favorite Myx Bandarito Performance {{small|(2006–2010; since 2018)}}
====Retired Awards==== *Myx Music Award for Favorite Indie Artist {{small|(2006–2011)}} *Myx Music Award for Favorite Myx Live Performance {{small|(2006–2013)}} *Myx Music Award for Favorite K-Pop Video {{small|(2011–2015)}}
===Special Awards=== *Myx Music Award for Myx Magna Award {{small|(since 2006)}} *Myx Music Award for Best Music Video {{small|(2016–2017)}} * Myx Music Award for Favorite Ringtone {{small|(2006–2008)}} *Special Citation
